{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0003","text":"像木頭 石頭難露出笑意","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["情感麻木","缺乏生氣"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["木頭","石頭","難","露出","笑意"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,2,0,0,2,3,4,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoeng6","muk6","tau4","sek6","tau4","naan4","lou6","ceot1","siu3","ji3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"木頭","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"石頭","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"難","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"露出","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"笑意","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"使用比喻（木頭、石頭）來形容情感上的僵硬和無法表達喜悅。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0004","text":"過往沒法明白我怎會到此","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["對過去的困惑","自我質疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["過往","沒法","明白","我","怎會","到此"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,2,4,0,2,5,9,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["gwo3","wong5","mut6","faat3","ming4","baak6","ngo5","zam2","dou3","ci2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"過往","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"沒法","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"明白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"怎會","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"此","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"表達對過去自己為何會處於這種狀態的困惑和不解。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0005","text":"活着然而又不滿意","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["對現狀的不滿","空虛感"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["活着","然而","不","滿意"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,0,2,3,5,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["wut6","zoek6","jin4","ji4","jau6","bat1","mun5","ji3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"活着","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"然而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"滿意","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"雖然活著，但對生活感到不滿意，進一步加深了負面情緒。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0006","text":"但自遇着你 我心跳躍不止","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的出現","重獲生機"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["遇着","你","心跳躍","不止"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,2,5,5,3,4,2,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","zi6","jyu6","zoek6","nei5","ngo5","sam1","tiu3","joek6","bat1","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"自遇","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"跳躍","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不止","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"轉折點，遇見「你」之後，內心重新燃起活力，心跳加速。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0007","text":"同行和同做平凡事","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["平凡的陪伴","共同經歷"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["同行","同做","平凡","事"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,0,0,2,0,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tung4","hang4","wo4","tung4","zou6","ping4","faan4","si6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"同行","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"和","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"同","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"做","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"平凡","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"事","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描述與「你」一起做平凡事情的狀態，強調陪伴感。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0008","text":"亦甚有意思 默默望着你","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["平凡中的意義","愛慕的目光"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["有意思","默默","望着","你"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,5,4,3,2,2,2,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jik6","sam6","jau5","ji3","si1","mak6","mak6","mong6","zoek6","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"甚","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"有意思","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"默默","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"望","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"即使是平凡的事情，因為有「你」而變得有意義，並表達默默注視的愛意。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0009","text":"我腦海似吐激光 全明瞭爲何生在此","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["豁然開朗","生命意義的覺醒"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["腦海","激光","明瞭","為何","生在此"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,9,5,4,3,3,0,0,0,0,3,2,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","nou5","hoi2","ci5","tou3","gik1","gwong1","cyun4","ming4","liu4","ho4","sang1","zoi6","ci2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"腦海","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"似吐","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"激光","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"全明","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"爲何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"生在","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"此","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"比喻手法，腦海中清晰地明白了生命的意義和存在的理由。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0010","text":"有你愛意指示 世界變了簡易","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的影響","世界的美好"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["愛意","指示","世界","變","簡易"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,4,4,9,2,4,4,4,5,9,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","nei5","oi3","ji3","zi2","si6","sai3","gaai3","bin3","liu5","gaan2","ji6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"愛意","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"指示","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"世界","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"變","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"簡易","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「你」的愛意指引，讓原本複雜的世界變得簡單美好。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0011","text":"有你愛意指示 雪裏要暖都易","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的溫暖","克服困難"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["愛意","指示","雪裏","暖","易"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,4,4,9,2,4,5,4,5,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","nei5","oi3","ji3","zi2","si6","syut3","leoi5","jiu3","nyun5","dou1","ji6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"愛意","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"指示","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"雪裏","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"暖","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"易","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"進一步強調「你」的愛意能帶來溫暖，甚至能克服極端的環境（雪裏要暖）。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
