{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0017","text":"但又胡亂大聲抗議","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["無謂的抗議","不滿情緒"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["胡亂","大聲","抗議"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,2,2,3,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","jau6","wu4","lyun6","daai6","sing1","kong3","ji5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"胡亂","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"大聲","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"抗議","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"描述過去不滿時的表現，是胡亂且大聲的抗議，缺乏建設性。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0018","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0018","text":"但自遇着你 我心抗議即止","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的轉變","停止抱怨"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["遇着","你","抗議","即止"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,2,5,5,3,4,5,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","zi6","jyu6","zoek6","nei5","ngo5","sam1","kong3","ji5","zik1","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"自遇","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"抗議","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"即止","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"轉折點，遇見「你」之後，過去的抗議行為立刻停止，顯示出積極的改變。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0019","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0019","text":"沿途如逢着麻煩事 亦我法子","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["面對困難的轉變","解決問題的能力"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["沿途","麻煩事","我","法子"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,0,0,2,0,0,2,2,5,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyun4","tou4","jyu4","fung4","zoek6","maa4","faan4","si6","jik6","ngo5","faat3","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"沿途","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"如逢","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"麻煩事","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"法子","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"即使遇到麻煩事，現在也有辦法解決，顯示出因「你」而來的積極轉變。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0020","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0020","text":"力量就是你 那眼中送我的癡","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的力量","被愛與珍惜"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["力量","就是","你","眼中","癡"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,0,2,2,5,5,5,3,4,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["lik6","loeng4","zau6","si6","nei5","naa5","ngaan5","zung1","sung3","ngo5","dik1","ci1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"力量","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"就是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"那","pos":"DET"},{"text":"眼中","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"送","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"癡","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"直接點明「你」是力量的來源，並感受到「你」眼中傳遞的愛意（癡）。"},"source":{"title":"ABC","artists":["草蜢"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1227","prev_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_6I2J6Jyi_MTIyNw_0021","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
